data.description: Huge Price Adjustment!! Location, location, location!! This is the ideal condo for individuals wishing to live in Clarendon/Court House. With a Walk Score of 96, this property is centrally located between Clarendon and Courthouse, with easy access to both Clarendon and Courthouse Metro stops.   Come see this open floor plan, freshly painted throughout, and features a huge principal bedroom, living/dining space, and a den that can be utilized as an office or guest bedroom. Stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. There is a washer and dryer in the unit. There are newer bathrooms and garage parking.  The balcony is a glass-enclosed extension of the living area that provides additional flex/office space as well as year-round use.   Concierge, 24x7 Fitness center,  Outdoor pool, Mail package room, Bike storage, and Community/Party Room with kitchen. Guest parking is a breeze with ample street parking and nearby garages. Enjoy super close proximity to Whole Foods Market, Starbucks, Courthaus Social, Arlington Rooftop Bar & Grill, Green Pig Bistro, The Apple Store, The Clarendon shopping mall, and MORE!!
